---
import TitleSection from '../../atomos/TitleSection.astro';
---

<section class="relative flex min-h-screen items-center justify-center px-6">
	<div class="flex max-w-4xl flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
		<span class="animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-0 mb-6 rounded-full border border-sky-400/30 bg-sky-400/10 px-4 py-1 text-sm text-sky-300">
			Network • HTTP • Status Codes
		</span>

		<TitleSection text="La Web se comunica mediante códigos de estado" align="center" color="white" size="text-3xl md:text-6xl" delay="animate-delay-100" />

		<p class="animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-200 mt-10 text-lg text-gray-400">
			Cada respuesta HTTP es una señal. Este flujo mantiene viva la comunicación en la web.
		</p>

		<div class="animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-300 mt-10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
			<span class="pill">200 OK</span>
			<span class="pill">302 Found</span>
			<span class="pill">404 Not Found</span>
			<span class="pill">503 Service Unavailable</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
